<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA83">
<l>varaikuṭaitōḷ kāmpāka vāniraikāt tāyar</l>
<l>niraiviṭaiyēḻ ceṟṟavā ṟeṉṉē – yuravuṭaiya</l>
<l>nīrāḻi yuṭkiṭantu nērā nicācararmēṟ</l>
<l>pērāḻi koṇṭa pirāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Which was the way that he protected the herd of cows with the mountain as an umbrella</l>
<l>[and his] arm as a shaft [and] subdued the seven bulls from the herds of the cowherds,</l>
<l>the lord who, lying in the ocean with powerful water, took up the big discus</l>
<l>against the hostile night-wandering [demons]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
